head.meta: Homepage for Irish Bouzouki/Mandolin/Octave Mandolin/Irish Tenor Banjo

provides: Irish-Trad.net provides free online resources and lessons for a variety of stringed instruments commonly found in traditional Irish sessions such as the Irish Bouzouki, Mandolin, Octave Mandola and Irish Tenor Banjo.
